title: Batgirl 23 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Batgirl 23

By:   	Gail Simone, Fernando Pasarin, Alex Garner	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Series:   	Batgirl
Publisher:   	DC Comics

The new "Batgirl: Wanted" epic begins here, as Commissioner Gordon must track down his son's murderer-who happens to be his daughter!

But has Barbara already given up the Bat?
